@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>Last updated: @DateTime.Now.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")</p>

<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>Welcome to <strong>NewsPaper Hub</strong>. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data while you browse and interact with our news platform.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> If you register on our platform, we may collect your name, email, and login credentials.</li>
    <li><strong>Browsing Data:</strong> We may collect non-personal data such as IP address, browser type, and reading preferences to enhance user experience.</li>
    <li><strong>Comments & Interactions:</strong> If you comment on articles or engage with news content, we may store your input and responses.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>Your data is used for the following purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>To provide access to news articles and personalized content.</li>
    <li>To improve website functionality and user experience.</li>
    <li>To send important updates, newsletters, or breaking news alerts (if subscribed).</li>
    <li>To analyze user preferences and enhance content recommendations.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
<p>We use cookies to remember user preferences, improve site navigation, and gather analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings if you prefer.</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We may collaborate with third-party services, such as analytics providers and ad networks, which may collect and process user data in accordance with their privacy policies.</p>

<h2>Data Security</h2>
<p>We implement security measures to protect user data from unauthorized access, breaches, or misuse. However, no online service can guarantee complete security.</p>

<h2>User Rights & Choices</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information.</li>
    <li>Unsubscribe from newsletters and marketing emails.</li>
    <li>Request a copy of the data we store about you.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Please check this page regularly for any changes.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at <strong>[Your Support Email]</strong>.</p>
